(241, 'Ruang Baca', 'ruang-baca', '<h3><b>RUANG BACA</b></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Jurusan Pengairan Universitas Brawijaya telah memiliki fasilitas ruang baca yang dapat di manfaatkan oleh seluruh civitas jurusan.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Berikut katalog buku koleksi ruang baca jurusan Teknik Pengairan yang bisa&nbsp;<a href=\"http://pengairan.ub.ac.id/s1/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/JUDUL-BUKU.xlsx\" target=\"_top\">diunduh</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://pengairan.ub.ac.id/s1/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/data-perpus.png\" target=\"_top\"><img alt=\"data-perpus\" height=\"258\" src=\"http://pengairan.ub.ac.id/s1/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/data-perpus-226x300.png\" width=\"195\" /></a><br />\r\n<em><strong>Data Per Juli 2013</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><b>Suasana Ruang Baca</b></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://pengairan.ub.ac.id/s1/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/1IMG_20130827_104619.jpg\" target=\"_top\"><img alt=\"1IMG_20130827_104619\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://pengairan.ub.ac.id/s1/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/1IMG_20130827_104619-225x300.jpg\" width=\"135\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://pengairan.ub.ac.id/s1/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/IMG_20130826_112407.jpg\" target=\"_top\"><img alt=\"IMG_20130826_112407\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://pengairan.ub.ac.id/s1/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/IMG_20130826_112407-225x300.jpg\" width=\"135\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://pengairan.ub.ac.id/s1/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/IMG_20130827_104215.jpg\" target=\"_top\"><img alt=\"IMG_20130827_104215\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://pengairan.ub.ac.id/s1/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/IMG_20130827_104215-225x300.jpg\" width=\"135\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://pengairan.ub.ac.id/s1/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/IMG_20130827_104342.jpg\" target=\"_top\"><img alt=\"IMG_20130827_104342\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://pengairan.ub.ac.id/s1/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/IMG_20130827_104342-225x300.jpg\" width=\"135\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://pengairan.ub.ac.id/s1/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/IMG_20130827_104510.jpg\" target=\"_